ce%20so%20far%20this%20year%20as%20well.%20Tech%20stocks%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20up%2015%25%20for%20the%20year%2C%20outstripping%20the%208%25%20gain%20in%20the%20broader%20index.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F2yejU%2F2%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Tech%20stocks%20racing%20ahead%20of%20S%26amp%3Bamp%3BP%20500%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22464%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETechnicals.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20market%20is%20also%20flashing%20some%20worrying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-correction-sp500-technical-analysis-bank-of-america-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etechnical%20signal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20El-Erian%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20note%2C%20Bank%20of%20America%20said%20there%20are%20numerous%20signs%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20is%20overstretched%2C%20such%20as%20the%20index%20recently%20diverging%20from%20momentum%20signals%20and%20flashing%20a%20technical%20%26quot%3Bexhaustion%20signal%26quot%3B%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20valuations%20got%20out%20of%20whack%2C%20technicals%20got%20out%20of%20whack%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20we're%20seeing%20today.%20It's%20technicals%20that%20are%20undermining%20the%20tech%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20El-Erian%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20selling%20pressure%20in%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEl-Erian%20also%20laid%20out%20two%20risk%20scenarios%20for%20markets%20that%20he%20sees%20brewing.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20is%20that%20the%20market%20could%20see%20a%20near-term%20%26quot%3Bair%20pocket%26quot%3B%20as%20