2C%20Kriti%20Sanon%20and%20Rashmika%20Mandanna%2C%20hit%20a%20speed%20bump%20on%20Day%2011%2C%20with%20collections%20dropping%20a%20steep%2060.2%25%20to%20Rs%201.75%20crore%20as%20the%20second-weekend%20bump%20faded%20and%20Welcome%20to%20the%20Jungle%20continued%20commanding%20the%20majority%20of%20screens%20nationwide.%20As%20Day%2012%20live%20tracking%20shows%20the%20film%20adding%20Rs%200.22%20crore%20so%20far%20across%201%2C360%20shows%2C%20the%20domestic%20net%20stands%20at%20Rs%2085.12%20crore%2C%20with%20the%20total%20India%20gross%20crossing%20the%20symbolic%20Rs%20100%20crore%20mark%20and%20the%20worldwide%20gross%20at%20Rs%20129.42%20crore.%20The%20film's%20path%20to%20a%20domestic%20Rs%20100%20crore%20net%20milestone%20is%20just%20roughly%20Rs%2015%20crore%20away%20even%20as%20the%20worldwide%20gross%20collection%20stands%20at%20Rs.%20129.42%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20CEO%20who%20once%20spent%203%20years%20in%20federal%20prison.%20Here's%20what%20I%20learned%20about%20bouncing%20back.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221402%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22T.%20Renee%20Smith%20wears%20a%20suit%20and%20sits%20at%20her%20desk%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a33f3dc564c774507cd4400%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221052%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ET.%20Renee%20Smith%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20iSuccess%20Consulting%2C%20a%20Georgia-based%20AI%20consultancy%20company.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20T.%20Renee%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIn%202007%2C%20T.%20Renee%20Smith%20was%20sentenced%20to%2046%20months%20in%20federal%20prison.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20being%20incarcerated%2C%20she%20had%20to%20rebuild%20her%20career.%20She's%20now%20CEO%20of%20an%20AI%20consultancy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20has%20three%20pieces%20of%20advice%20for%20bouncing%20back%3A%20grieve%2C%20accept%2C%20and%20shift%20your%20mindset.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20T.%20Renee%20Smith%2C%2051%2C%20who%20is%20based%20in%20Atlanta.%20She%20is%20CEO%20of%20iSuccess%20Consulting.%20In%202007%2C%20she%20was%20sentenced%20to%2046%20months%20in%20federal%20prison%20for%20conspiring%20to%20use%20false%20financial%20information%20to%20obtain%20bank%20loans.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20her%20sentence%20and%20employment.%20This%20piece%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20happened%20at%20once.%20In%20the%20space%20of%20a%20year%2C%20I%20got%20married%2C%20pregnant%2C%20and%20started%20serving%20my%20prison%20sentence.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20business%20partner%20and%20I%20ran%20communication%20businesses%2C%20made%20some%20very%20bad%20decisions%2C%20and%20my%20life%20spiraled%20out%20of%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20charged%20with%20a%20felony%20in%202005.%20In%20the%20roughly%20two%20years%20it%20took%20to%20go%20to%20court%2C%20I%20met%20my%20husband%20and%20got%20married.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20was%20sentenced%20in%202007%2C%20I%20was%20four%20months%20pregnant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20night%20of%20my%2046-month%20sentence%20in%20late%202007%20felt%20like%20an%20out-of-body%20experience%20where%20I%20was%20looking%20at%20my%20life%20from%20the%20outside%2C%20feeling%20sad%20for%20that%20woman.%20My%20son%20was%20born%20in%20April%202008%20and%20spent%20the%20first%2011%20months%20with%20me%20in%20prison.%20Then%20he%20went%20to%20live%20with%20my%20husband%20and%20parents.%20It%20was%20a%20psychologically%20challenging%20time%20for%20all%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20in%20prison%20stripped%20me%20of%20everything%20I%20thought%20was%20important%2C%20and%20I%20had%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmotherhood-identity-crisis-career-coach-new-jobs-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eidentity%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20who%20I%20was%20outside%20my%20role%20as%20a%20business%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20see%20my%20incarceration%20as%20an%20opportunity%3A%20I%20had%20to%20come%20out%20better%20on%20the%20other%20side%2C%20to%20make%20something%20great%20out%20of%20a%20bad%20situation.%20When%20I%20was%20released%2C%20I%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-became-empty-nester-reinvented-life-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erebuild%20my%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20reinvent%20myself%20with%20a%20felony%20to%20my%20name.%20I%20eventually%20got%20there%2C%20and%20now%20I'm%20the%20CEO%20of%20an%20AI%20consultancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22adfa691b-e2a2-4a80-ad74-8b3dd19e5c04%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERebuilding%20my%20career%20after%20a%20break%20wasn't%20easy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20released%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20late%202010%2C%20the%20reality%20that%20I%20likely%20wasn't%20going%20to%20be%20hired%20for%20any%20corporate%20positions%20with%20a%20felony%20hit%20me%20hard.%20I%20realized%20I'd%20have%20to%20start%20a%20business%20for%20my%20livelihood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20had%20tunnel%20vision%20about%20rebuilding%20myself%2C%20and%20my%20attitude%20was%3A%20let's%20go.%20What%20I%20didn't%20realize%20was%3A%20sweetie%2C%20you've%20been%20away%20for%20years.%20You%20have%20to%20reintegrate%20into%20your%20family%20and%20your%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20such%20a%20setback%2C%20you%20need%20time%20to%20acclimatize%20and%20reinvent%20yourself%2C%20which%20I%20didn't%20give%20myself%2C%20because%20I%20just%20threw%20myself%20back%20into%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222496%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Speaker%20gestures%20onstage%20beside%20a%20red%20presentation%20slide%20reading%20%26quot%3BWomen%20in%20Leadership.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a33f49d4074dae0e20456c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221664%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmith%20had%20to%20rebuild%20her%20career%20after%20time%20in%20a%20federal%20prison.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20T.%20Renee%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20with%20contract%20work%20that%20didn't%20require%20background%20checks%2C%20while%20setting%20up%20a%20consulting%20business%20on%20the%20side%20in%202011.%20It%20was%20a%20slow%20build%2C%20but%20over%20a%20few%20years%2C%20clients%20referred%20me%20to%20other%20clients%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsc%2Fhow-to-grow-a-small-business%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20business%20grew%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20rebuilt%20my%20life%20and%20business%20from%20the%20ground%20up.%20Now%2C%20as%20an%20AI%20transformation%20strategist%20and%20the%20CEO%20of%20iSuccess%20Consulting%2C%20I%20help%20clients%20assess%20their%20AI%20readiness%2C%20develop%20implementation%20strategies%2C%20and%20make%20sure%20their%20workforce%20is%20prepared%20for%20those%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226bcaa5c6-264e-4824-8358-a28773ab2328%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%203%20pieces%20of%20advice%3A%20grieve%2C%20practice%20acceptance%2C%20and%20shift%20your%20mindset%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHopefully%2C%20others%20don't%20have%20reasons%20like%20mine%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-worker-shares-why-she-took-career-break-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20career%20break%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20many%20people%20have%20stories%20where%20life%20turns%20out%20differently%20than%20they%20planned.%20Whether%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcaring-for-independent-mother-after-stroke-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebecoming%20a%20caregiver%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20going%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgot-divorced-knew-nothing-about-finances-job-what-to-do-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20divorce%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20losing%20a%20child%2C%20or%20being%20laid%20off%2C%20many%20people%20end%20up%20needing%20to%20find%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconan-obrien-mindset-overcoming-failure-career-setbacks-hollywood-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eways%20to%20bounce%20back%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20these%20people%20rebuilding%20after%20a%20setback%2C%20I%20believe%20my%20advice%20applies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20grieve%20the%20life%20you%20thought%20you'd%20have.%20Secondly%2C%20replace%20the%20belief%20that%20your%20life%20%26quot%3Bshould%20have%26quot%3B%20turned%20out%20a%20certain%20way%20with%20acceptance%20of%20how%20it%20is.%20Instead%20of%20wishing%20my%20life%20were%20something%20else%2C%20I%20ask%20myself%20what%20lesson%20I%20needed%20to%20learn%20from%20it%20and%20how%20I%20could%20grow%20from%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20shifting%20your%20mindset.%20If%20I'd%20looked%20at%20myself%20and%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20convicted%20felon.%20Nobody's%20going%20to%20hire%20me.%20I%20can't%20build%20a%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20then%20I%20would've%20become%20my%20own%20worst%20enemy.%20I%20had%20to%20shift%20my%20mindset%20to%20my%20current%20situation%20and%20ask%3A%20how%20did%20that%20break%20help%20you%2C%20what%20did%20you%20learn%20from%20it%2C%20and%20what%20do%20you%20need%20to%20build%20your%20new%20life%20afterward%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20life%20has%20been%20an%20absolute%20journey%2C%20but%20I%20wouldn't%20change%20anything%20because%20it%20made%20me%20who%20I%20am%20today.%20There's%20no%20way%20that%20I'd%20be%20as%20resilient%20as%20I%20if%20I%20wasn't%20incarcerated.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-year-in-federal-prison-how-to-bounce-back-2026-6%5C%