ed%20with%20snacks.%20Meta%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fandrew-bosworth-meta-employees-unrest%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%20trying%20to%20improve%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20microkitchens%20amid%20morale%20challenges%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20tech%20companies%20rethink%20workplace%20perks%20in%20an%20era%20of%20AI%20and%20cost%20discipline%2C%20Nvidia's%20understated%20approach%20has%20become%20less%20of%20an%20outlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20employees%20attributed%20the%20approach%20to%20different%20facets%20of%20Nvidia's%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPhilosophically%2C%20I%20think%20Jensen%20has%20a%20general%20belief%20about%20separation%20of%20pleasure%20and%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20said%2C%20noting%20the%20company%20didn't%20have%20%26quot%3Bping-pong%20tables%2C%20a%20company%20gym%2C%20massages-on-request%2C%20or%20stuff%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20added%20that%20Huang%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-street-food-influencer-taiwan-china-korea-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20noted%20foodie%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20wants%20employees%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20their%20%26quot%3Blife's%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20requires%20a%20healthy%20balance.%20%26quot%3BOther%20workplaces%20where%20everything%20is%20free%20are%20implicitly%20trying%20to%20coax%20employees%20into%20staying%20in%20the%20office%20as%20much%20as%20possible%20%E2%80%94%20Nvidia%20has%20the%20exact%20opposite%20philosophy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20frugal%20is%20deeply%20rooted%20in%20Nvidia's%20DNA%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20third%20employee%20who%20no%20longer%20works%20at%20the%20company.%20%26quot%3BTraditionally%2C%20hardware%20companies%20have%20always%20been%20operating%20at%20very%20thin%20margins%2C%20far%20below%20what%20software%20companies%20were%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20this%