%2F%3Fp%3D1236798177%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20leading%20Indian%20film%20on%20IMDb%20heading%20into%20the%20year%E2%80%99s%20second%20half%20is%20Nitesh%20Tiwari%E2%80%99s%20epic%20adaptation%20%E2%80%9CRamayana%20Part%201%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20claimed%20the%20top%20position%20on%20the%20platform%E2%80%99s%20Most%20Anticipated%20Indian%20Movies%20list%20for%20July%20through%20December.%20The%2020-title%20ranking%20was%20compiled%20from%20page%20views%20logged%20by%20IMDb%E2%80%99s%20more%20than%20250%20million%20monthly%20visitors%20between%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Naman%20Ramachandran%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20says%20gas%20companies%20should%20lower%20prices%20to%20%242.50%20a%20gallon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22U.S.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20speaks%20to%20the%20media%20as%20he%20departs%20after%20meeting%20with%20Republican%20senators%20at%20the%20U.S.%20Capitol%20on%20June%2024%2C%202026%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a432494a25092c74cca129e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223805%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrump%20said%20gas%20retailers%20need%20to%20drop%20prices%20to%20%242.50%20per%20gallon.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Dietsch%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDonald%20Trump%20criticized%20gas%20retailers%20for%20keeping%20prices%20high%20for%20Americans.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20retailers%20need%20to%20stop%20gouging%20customers%20and%20bring%20prices%20down%20to%20%242.50%20a%20gallon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20nationwide%20gas%20average%20stood%20at%20%243.86%20per%20gallon%20as%20of%20Monday%2C%20per%20the%20AAA.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20slammed%20gasoline%20retailers%20for%20failing%20to%20lower%20prices%20for%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Monday%20evening%20Truth%20Social%20post%2C%20Trump%20wrote%20that%20the%20retailers%20must%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-prices-worsening-k-shaped-economy-research-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elower%20prices%20immediately%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20they%20are%20too%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20no%20gauging%2C%20which%20is%20totally%20illegal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20likely%20referring%20to%20gouging%2C%20the%20act%20of%20overcharging%20customers.%20%26quot%3BIf%20retailers%20don't%20do%20this%2C%20big%20problems%20lie%20ahead!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20retailers%20should%20%26quot%3Bstart%20targeting%20around%20the%20%242.50%20a%20gallon%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20warned%20that%20California%20should%20stop%20charging%20heavy%20taxes%20on%20its%20gasoline.%20The%20state%20is%20set%20to%20increase%20the%20gas%20tax%20rate%20from%2061.4%20cents%20per%20gallon%20to%2063.4%20cents%20per%20gallon%20on%20July%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Monday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-prices-high-how-to-save-money-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaverage%20gas%20price%3C%2Fa%3E%20nationwide%20stood%20at%20%243.86%20per%20gallon%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20American%20Automobile%20Association.%20California%20and%20Hawaii%20currently%20have%20the%20highest%20gas%20prices%20in%20the%20country%2C%20at%20%245.45%20and%20%245.49%20per%20gallon%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20Truth%20Social%20post%20comes%20about%20a%20week%20after%20he%20slammed%20big%20oil%20companies%20for%20keeping%20oil%20prices%20high%20despite%20easing%20tensions%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20and%20the%20reopening%20of%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20big%20Oil%20Companies%20are%20not%20dropping%20their%20price%20at%20the%20pump%20commensurate%20with%20the%20sharply%20lower%20prices%20they%20are%20paying%20for%20Oil.%20Those%20prices%20are%20dropping%20like%20a%20rock!%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20had%20instructed%20the%20Justice%20Department%20to%20investigate%20oil%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChevron's%20finance%20chief%20Eimear%20Bonner%20told%20CNBC%20on%20Thursday%20that%20energy%20providers%20were%20doing%20what%20they%20could%2C%20but%20it%20would%20take%20time%20for%20prices%20to%20come%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20take%20time%2C%20though.%20There%20is%20a%20lag%20between%2C%20you%20know%2C%20oil%20prices%20and%20reductions%20in%20oil%20prices%2C%20and%20when%20that%20shows%20up%20at%20the%20pump%2C%20but%20we%20expect%20that%20prices%20will%20come%20down%20as%20things%20continue%20to%20normalize%2C%26quot%3B%20Bonner%20told%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGas%20prices%20have%20skyrocketed%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20US-Iran%20war%20in%20February%2C%20with%20the%20nationwide%20average%20climbing%20to%20well%20above%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgas-prices-drop-below-4-gallon-first-time-in-months-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%244%20per%20gallon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20per%20the%20AAA.%20They%20have%20come%20down%20slightly%20after%20peace%20talks%20with%20Iran%20were%20initiated%2C%20and%20after%20Trump%20announced%20a%20ceasefire%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-gas-companies-must-lower-prices-warning-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782793185000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4324c3e218c3b62535f07b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-gas-companies-must-lower-prices-warning-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20average%20nationwide%20gas%20price%20stood%20at%20%243.86%20per%20gallon%20as%20of%20Monday%2C%20according%20to%20the%20AAA.