wer%20taxes%20and%20a%20friendlier%20regulatory%20environment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20battle%20traffic%20to%20get%20to%20work.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flife-of-uber-ceo-travis-kalanick-2017-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETravis%20Kalanick%3C%2Fa%3E%20appears%20to%20be%20skipping%20it%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Uber%20cofounder%20and%20former%20CEO%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20X%20on%20Monday%20showing%20what%20he%20called%20his%20%26quot%3B5%20minute%20jet%20ski%20commute%26quot%3B%20across%20Lake%20Austin%20to%20his%20new%20office%2C%20giving%20followers%20a%20glimpse%20of%20his%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eunconventional%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.x.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFirst%20day%20at%20our%20new%20Austin%20office.%20Video%20of%20my%205%20minute%20jet%20ski%20commute%20to%20work..%20%F0%9F%98%8F%F0%9F%98%85%F0%9F%98%82%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FxMT0C85vW3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FxMT0C85vW3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20travis%20kalanick%20(%40travisk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Ftravisk%2Fstatus%2F2071614503804948670%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2029%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EKalanick%20is%20now%20based%20in%20Texas%2C%20where%20he%20owns%20a%20home%20on%20Lake%20Austin.%20The%20billionaire%20entrepreneur%20said%20on%20the%20TBPN%20podcast%20in%20March%20that%20he%20has%20owned%20the%20place%20for%20five%20years%2C%20drawn%20in%20part%20by%20the%20lake%20and%20his%20love%20of%20watersports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20growing%20list%20of%20tech%20leaders%20who%20have%20traded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-uber-ceo-travis-kalanick-said-he-moved-to-texas-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESilicon%20Valley%20for%20Texas%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Billionaires%20and%20companies%20alike%20have%20been%20drawn%20by%20lower%20taxes%2C%20cheaper%20real%20estate%2C%20and%20a%20friendlier%20regulatory%20climate%20than%20California%2C%20where%20rising%20costs%20and%20talk%20of%20a%20one-time%20billionaire%20wealth%20tax%20have%20rattled%20some%20executives.%20Tesla%2C%20Oracle%2C%20and%20Hewlett-Packard%20Enterprise%20are%20among%20the%20companies%20that%20have%20shifted%20major%20operations%20to%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalanick%20is%20now%20leading%20Atoms%2C%20the%20newly%20renamed%20version%20of%20City%20Storage%20Systems%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravis-kalanick-cloudkitchens-picnic-mixt-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eparent%20company%20of%20CloudKitchens%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20startup%20is%20developing%20AI-powered%20robots%20designed%20to%20automate%20repetitive%20physical%20work%20in%20industries%20such%20as%20food%20service%2C%20mining%2C%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20logistics.%20He%20previously%20described%20Atoms'%20goal%20as%20building%20%26quot%3Bgainfully%20employed%20robots%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20take%20on%20specialized%20tasks%20at%20an%20industrial%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalanick%20co-founded%20Uber%20in%202009%20and%20helped%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20ride-hailing%20giant%20before%20resigning%20in%202017.%20Since%20then%2C%20he's%20been%20focused%20on%20building%20software%20and%20robotics%20for%20kitchens%2C%20mining%2C%20and%20logistics.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20his%20move%20to%20Austin%20gives%20him%20the%20choice%20of%20several%20robotaxis%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20Kalanick%20will%20be%20boating%20his%20way%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravis-kalanick-lake-austin-commute-jet-ski-ride-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness