0heard%20evidence%20that%20the%20director%2C%20instead%20of%20delivering%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-director-carl-rinsch-white-horse-footage-concept-trial-exhibits-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ean%20ambitious%20sci-fi%20epic%20called%20%26quot%3BWhite%20Horse%26quot%3B%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Netflix%2C%20went%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-director-carl-rinsch-spending-spree-postmates-uber-eats-deliveries-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20luxury%20spending%20spree%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20included%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcarl-rinsch-netflix-fraud-trial-hermes-hastens-mattress-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20%24439%2C000%20handmade%20H%C3%A4stens%20mattress%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20District%20Judge%20Jed%20Rakoff%20pushed%20back%20against%20a%20prosecutor%20who%20argued%20that%20Rinsch%20was%20motivated%20solely%20by%20greed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20had%20purchased%20one%20Rolls-Royce%2C%20or%20even%20maybe%20the%20Rolls-Royce%20and%20the%20Ferrari%2C%20that%20would%20have%20been%20at%20least%20consistent%20with%20the%20view%20you're%20now%20expressing%2C%26quot%3B%20Rakoff%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20he%20purchased%20five%20Rolls-Royces%20plus%20the%20Ferrari.%20That%20suggests%20someone%20who%20is%20not%20operating%20solely%20from%20greed%2C%20but%20also%20someone%20who's%20got%20a%20kind%20of%20manic%20state%20of%20mind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20director's%20conduct%20was%20egregious%2C%20the%20judge%20said.%20There%20was%20overwhelming%20proof%20that%20Rinsch%20had%20lied%20about%20his%20conduct%2C%20Rakoff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20chose%20to%20do%20this.%20And%20he%20chose%20to%20continue%20it%20and%20to%20cover%20it%20up%20for%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Rakoff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERinsch%2C%20wearing%20a%20blue%20suit%20with%20a%20salmon%20tie%20and%20matching%20pocket%20square%2C%20told%20Rakoff%20that%20the%20experience%20of%20going%20through%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20forced%20him%20%26quot%3Bto%20confront%20things%20about%20my%20life%20and%20my%20health%20that%20I%20have%20been%20unable%20to%20confront%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20was%20receiving%20mental%20health%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20spend%20every%20day%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%20working%20to%20restore%20the%20trust%20I've%20lost%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20lower%20Manhattan%20courtroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20attorneys%2C%20Daniel%20McGuinness%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20looked%20forward%20to%20appealing%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20brought%20fraud%20charges%20against%20him%20following%20the%20collapse%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-director-carl-rinsch-white-horse-footage-concept-trial-exhibits-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BWhite%20Horse%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20science%20fiction%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20clonelike%20beings%20that%20form%20their%20own%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20initially%20agreed%20to%20pay%20%2444%20million%20for%20Rinsch%20to%20deliver%20about%2013%20short%20episodes%20of%20the%20show.%20The%20director%20was%20a%20prot%C3%A9g%C3%A9%20of%20%26quot%3BBlade%20Runner%26quot%3B%20director%20Ridley%20Scott%20and%20had%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkeanu-reeves-prison-sentence-letter-netflix-carl-rinsch-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esupport%20of%20Keanu%20Reeves%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whom%20he%20had%20directed%20in%20the%202013%20movie%20%26quot%3B47%20Ronin.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20project%20went%20over%20budget%2C%20Netflix%20agreed%20to%20pay%20Rinsch%20another%20%2411%20million%20to%20complete%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFilming%20never%20picked%20up%20again.%20Rinsch%20moved%20the%20money%20through%20a%20series%20of%20bank%20accounts%2C%20invested%20in%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20and%20bought%20luxury%20goods.%20At%20trial%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-director-carl-rinsch-testifies-11-million-fraud-trial-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERinsch%20testified%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20believed%20the%20additional%20funds%20were%20mostly%20backpay%20for%20him%20paying%20out%20of%20pocket%20for%20earlier%20cost%20overruns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%20found%20Rinsch%20guilty%20in%20December.%20Before%20the%20sentencing%2C%20Reeves%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkeanu-reeves-prison-sentence-letter-netflix-carl-rinsch-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewrote%20a%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20asking%20the%20judge%20to%20show%20leniency%2C%20saying%20that%20Rinsch%20tended%20to%20self-sabotage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20prison%20sentence%2C%20Rakoff%20ordered%20Rinsch%20to%20pay%20%2411%20million%20in%20restitution%2C%20plus%20legal%20fees%20Netflix%20incurred%20assisting%20prosecutors%20and%20preparing%20executives%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-peter-friedlander-testifies-director-carl-rinsch-fruad-trial-2025-12%2522%253etestified%2520in%2520the%2520criminal%2520trial%253c%2Fa%253e.%2520Rinsch%2520separately%2520owes%2520Netflix%2520millions%2520of%2520dollars%2520in%2520a%2520related%2520civil%2520dispute%2520over%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Netflix%20declined%20to%20comment.%20Rinsch%20declined%20to%20comment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20McGuinness%20noted%20the%20tall%20odds%20of%20Rinsch%20ever%20repaying%20the%20money%20he%20owed%20to%20Netflix.%20It%20is%20%26quot%3Bpreposterous%26quot%3B%20to%20think%20any%20Hollywood%20studio%20would%20give%20him%20millions%20of%20dollars%20for%20anything%20ever%20again%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20he%20has%20some%20career%2C%20some%20creative%20outlet%2C%26quot%3B%20McGuinness%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20nowhere%20near%20the%20scope%20he%20had%20in%20the%20past.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-director-carl-rinsch-sentenced-2-half-years-prison-fraud-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782769496000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42b8bae218c3b62535edd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-director-carl-rinsch-sentenced-2-half-years-prison-fraud-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20judge%20said%20Carl%20Rinsch%20may%20have%20been%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bmanic%20state%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20bought%20five%20Rolls-Royces%20and%20a%20Ferrari%20but%20he%20spent%20years%20covering%20it%20up.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jshamsian%40businessinsider.com%20(Jacob%20Shamsian)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A93%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Persona%E2%80%99%20Live-Action%20TV%20Adaptation%20in%20the%20Works%20at%20Netflix%2C%2021%20Laps%20%26amp%3B%20Story%20Kitchen%20to%20Produce%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782768600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236798581%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Netflix%20is%20developing%20a%20live-action%20series%20based%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9CPersona%E2%80%9D%20video%20game%20franchise%2C%20Variety%20has%20learned%20from%20sources.%20Christopher%20Monfette%20is%20attached%20to%20write%20the%20adaptation%20in%20addition%20to%20serving%20as%20executive%20producer%20and%20showrunner.%20Shawn%20Levy%20and%20Robert%20Atwood%20of%2021%20Laps%20will%20also%20executive%20produce%20along%20with%20Dmitri%20M.%20Johnson%2C%20Michael%