im%2C%20and%20Alana%20Haim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwift%20and%20HAIM's%20relationship%20seemingly%20began%20online%20in%20the%20early%202010s%20after%20both%20of%20them%20tweeted%20about%20their%20love%20for%20one%20another's%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwift%20hung%20out%20with%20the%20band%20at%20a%20Golden%20Globes%20party%20in%20January%202015%2C%20and%20later%20that%20month%2C%20they%20all%20took%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teenvogue.com%2Fstory%2Ftaylor-swift-haim-hawaii-vacation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrip%20to%20Hawaii%20together%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwift%20invited%20the%20band%20to%20open%20for%20her%201989%20tour%20later%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20sisters%20have%20collaborated%20with%20Swift%20many%20times%20over%20the%20years%20%E2%80%94%20and%20have%20been%20regularly%20spotted%20hanging%20out%20with%20her.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224117%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taylor%20Swift%20on%20stage%20with%20the%20Haim%20sisters%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42d255a25092c74cca115c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222782%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Haim%20sisters%20performed%20during%20the%20Eras%20Tour.%3Cp%3EJeff%20Kravitz%2FTAS23%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20TAS%20Rights%20Management%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20band%20has%20continued%20touring%2C%20making%20music%2C%20and%20hanging%20out%20with%20Swift%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20band%20collaborated%20with%20Swift%20on%20her%20album%20%26quot%3BEvermore.%26quot%3B%20They%20were%20featured%20on%20the%20track%20%26quot%3BNo%20Body%2C%20No%20Crime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20dream%20of%20singing%20on%20a%20country%20folk%20song%20with%20the%20one%20and%20only%20queen%20of%20storytelling%2C%20miss%20Taylor%20Swift%20is%20our%20second%20Hanukkah%20present%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20wrote%20in%20an%20Instagram%20post%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202021%2C%20Swift%20posted%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLe2TODD5ey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephoto%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20herself%20and%20the%20Haim%20sisters%20hanging%20out%20in%20footie%20pajamas%20and%20eating%20pizza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20May%2C%20Swift%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCOwDSl7jjVv%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20a%20picture%20of%20them%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0hanging%20out%20with%20the%20caption%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20meet%20up%20every%20Tuesday%20night%20for%20dinner%20and%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lyric%20from%20%26quot%3BNo%20Body%2C%20No%20Crime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20band%20showed%20their%20support%20for%20%26quot%3BRed%20(Taylor's%20Version)%26quot%3B%20on%20Instagram%20stories%20in%20November%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202022%2C%20Swift%20surprised%20fans%20by%20appearing%20on%20stage%20with%20Haim%20at%20the%20band's%20concert%20in%20London.%20They%20performed%20a%20mash-up%20of%20Haim's%20%26quot%3BGasoline%26quot%3B%20and%20Swift's%20%26quot%3BLove%20Story%26quot%3B%20in%20matching%20leather%20pants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Swift%20released%20a%20teaser%20trailer%20for%20her%20%26quot%3BMidnights%26quot%3B%20music%20videos%20that%20year%2C%20the%20Haim%20sisters%20were%20credited%20at%20the%20end.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sister%20group%20joined%20as%20an%20opening%20act%20for%20a%20leg%20of%20Swift's%20Eras%20Tour%2C%20and%20they%20were%20also%20photographed%20hanging%20out%20with%20Swift%20on%20her%20days%20off.%20They%20also%20celebrated%20the%20Fourth%20of%20July%20with%20Swift%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202026%2C%20Swift%20was%20also%20photographed%20with%20the%20sisters%20%E2%80%94%20wearing%20matching%20punny%20Kicks%20shirts%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20NBA%20Finals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESwift%20and%20Lena%20Dunham's%20friendship%20seemi