3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Pfc.%20Peter%20Bannister%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20Army%20is%20eyeing%20drone%20boats%20to%20help%20fix%20its%20watercraft%20logistics%20problem.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Army's%20watercraft%20fleet%20for%20carrying%20personnel%20and%20supplies%20has%20shrunk%20and%20declined%20in%20readiness.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20service%20anticipates%20testing%20one%20autonomous%20vessel%20sometime%20next%20summer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Army%20is%20interested%20in%20acquiring%20drone%20boats%20to%20supplement%20its%20limited%20fleet%20of%20supply%20and%20transport%20watercraft%20in%20the%20Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20faces%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmy-reviewing-plan-to-divest-get-rid-of-boats-watercraft-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efleet%20size%20and%20readiness%20problems%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20its%20watercraft.%20Uncrewed%20surface%20vessels%2C%20or%20USVs%2C%20are%20seen%20as%20a%20potential%20solution%20that%20could%20relieve%20the%20logistics%20strain%20on%20crewed%20watercraft%2C%20operating%20in%20more%20forward-deployed%20environments%20and%20quickly%20dispatching%20supplies%2C%20weapons%2C%20and%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20reporters%20at%20a%20media%20roundtable%20last%20week%2C%20Maj.%20Gen.%20Gavin%20Gardner%2C%20head%20of%208th%20Theater%20Sustainment%20Command%2C%20said%20the%20Army%20anticipates%20testing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-rehearsed-sea-drone-rescues-apache-downed-real-mission-began-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edrone%20boat%3C%2Fa%3E%20sometime%20as%20early%20as%20next%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20Army%20could%20ultimately%20end%20up%20buying%20a%20fleet%20of%20anywhere%20between%2030%20and%20100%20medium-sized%20vessels%20capable%20of%20carrying%20eight%20to%20ten%2020-foot%20containers.%20He%20didn't%20identify%20companies%20involved%20but%20said%20that%20some%20firms%20had%20traveled%20to%20the%20region%20and%20demonstrated%20some%20of%20their%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20future%20autonomous%20vessels%20could%20range%20in%20size%20and%20use%2C%20but%20larger%20ones%20would%20need%20to%20be%20capable%20of%20carrying%20shipping%20containers%2C%20supplies%2C%20and%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20see%20those%20operating%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-new-pacific-command-built-for-a-complex-fight-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20PACOM%20%3C%2Fa%3Earea%20of%20responsibility%2C%26quot%3B%20Gardner%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20US%20Pacific%20Command%2C%20which%20oversees%20military%20operations%20in%20the%20region.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20gives%20you%20a%20ton%20of%20operations%2C%20inventory%20in%20motion%2C%20easy%20to%20respond.%20And%20then%20because%20they're%20autonomous%2C%20and%20we%20can%20work%20with%20our%20partner%20nations%20forward%2C%20you%20have%20those%20berthed%20up%20everywhere%20from%20Korea%20to%20Japan%2C%20the%20Philippines%2C%20Australia%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Thailand%2C%20etc.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20vessels%20could%20be%20controlled%20from%20the%20command's%20headquarters%20in%20Hawaii%20but%20would%20likely%20be%20forward-deployed%20in%20response%20to%20a%20constant%20demand%20on%20Army%20vessels%20to%20deliver%20supplies%20and%20equipment%20in%20the%20Pacific%20area%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221957%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20drone%20boat%20sails%20in%20the%20blue%20ocean.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42cb49a25092c74cca110d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221305%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrone%20boats%20could%20supplement%20crewed%20watercraft%2C%20but%20the%20Army%20doesn't%20anticipate%20replacing%20its%20fleet%20with%20uncrewed%20vessels.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Pfc.%20Jose%20Nunez%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20expectation%20is%20that%20the%20first%20contracted%20vessel%20would%20head%20out%20to%20Hawaii%20this%20time%20next%20year%20and%20assist%20in%20moving%20equipment%20and%20supplies%20in%20the%20Hawaiian%20islands%20for%20evaluation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Army's%20watercraft%20problem%20has%20long%20been%20a%20challenge%20for%20the%20service.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%202024%2C%20the%20US%20Government%20Accountability%20Office%2C%20a%20congressional%20watchdog%2C%20reported%20that%20the%20mission-capable%20rate%20of%20the%20Army's%2070%20watercraft%20had%20slid%20from%20more%20than%2070%25%20in%202020%20to%20less%20than%2040%25%20in%202024%2C%20partially%20due%20to%20long-standing%20maintenance%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20service%20is%20currently%20working%20to%20address%20problems%20with%20its%20fleet%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20ways%20beyond%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-company-long-range-drone-ships-china-war-tested-tech-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eautonomous%20surface%20vessels%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%202024%2C%20the%20Army%20activated%20its%20first%20new%20composite%20watercraft%20company%20in%20decades%2C%20and%20it%20has%20plans%20to%20receive%20a%20total%20of%20seven%20Maneuver%20Support%20Vessels%20(Light)%3B%20one%20is%20currently%20in%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20composite%20watercraft%20company%20is%20set%20to%20be%20activated%20in%20October%2C%20Gardner%20said%2C%20and%20one%20potentially%20consisting%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-commander-nato-developing-naval-drones-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eautonomous%20and%20crewed%20vessels%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20be%20ready%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20doesn't%20view%20USVs%20as%20a%20wholesale%20replacement%20of%20crewed%20watercraft%20but%20rather%20a%20complement.%20%26quot%3BI%20use%20autonomous%20watercraft%20to%20do%20routine%20delivery%2C%20and%20then%20I%20see%20my%20manned%20Army%20watercraft%20systems%20to%20really%20give%20commanders%20operational%20maneuver%20to%20deliver%20at%20the%20time%20and%20place%20of%20our%20choosing%2C%20on%20the%20beach%2C%20that%20maybe%20an%20autonomous%20watercraft%20doesn't%20have%20the%20capability%20to%20do%2C%20but%20current%20Army%20watercraft%20systems%20are%20designed%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20command%20is%20also%20looking%20at%20pulling%20prepositioned%20watercraft%20out%20of%20storage%2C%20using%20contractor-owned%20and%20-operated%20vessels%2C%20training%20Army%20personnel%20on%20those%20contractor%20vessels%2C%20and%20relying%20on%20allies%20like%20Japan%20and%20the%20Philippines%20for%20assistance%20to%20address%20shortfalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-looking-to-drone-boats-help-pacific-watercraft-problems-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782764045000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42cc4be218c3b62535eef1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-looking-to-drone-boats-help-pacific-watercraft-problems-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Autonomous%20vessels%20could%20help%20transport%20supplies%20and%20equipment%2C%20supplementing%20the%20Army's%20limited%20fleet%20of%20crewed%20watercraft.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpanella%40businessinsider.com%20(Chris%20Panella)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A92%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jacob%20Elordi%20or%20Callum%20Turner%20Should%20Not%20Be%20James%20Bond%2C%20Says%20Ex-007%20Casting%20Director%3A%20%E2%80%98We%20Know%20So%20Much%20About%20Them%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20Actor%20Should%20Be%20%E2%80%98Out%20of%20the%20Blue%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782764